data.title: A Door into Ocean by Joan Slonczewski (English) Paperback Book 9780312876524
data.meta_description: A Door into Ocean by Joan Slonczewski. Joan Slonczewski's A Door into Ocean is the novel upon which the author's reputation as an important SF writer principally rests. Joan Slonczewski lives in Gambier, Ohio and teaches biology at Kenyon College.
data.text: Will ship within 10 business days of receiving cleared payment. The seller has specified an extended handling time for this item.
